  "plan": "1) Inspect current /app contents. 2) Create/overwrite /app/index.html implementing the React app via CDN (React, ReactDOM, Babel). 3) Implement Markdown parsing (headers + first non-empty sentence under each). 4) Implement lightweight PDF text extraction by scanning decoded bytes for text in parentheses and joining it (good enough for simple fixtures), ensuring fileType becomes 'pdf'. 5) Implement analysis functions: citation regex, deterministic word counting via /\b[\w'-]+\b/g, keyword counts/density rounded to 3 decimals. 6) Render UI with required section titles and JSON mirror. 7) Quick local sanity check by opening the file list and grepping for required IDs/headers.",
